page.title: 01Introduction
page.content: This Block comprises an area of north-west central London.It contains a number of nationally known place,such as Hyde Park,Regent's Park,Kensington Palace,Little Venice,Marylebone and Paddington Stations.The boroughs included in this block are West Kilburn,Maida Vale,St.John's Wood, Paddington and Bayswater. The contents of the text pages are as follows:-1.Introduction.2.Padington and Royalty.3.Round Pond,Peter Pan.4.Hyde Park.5.Hyde Park.6.Queen's Park and Kensal Town.7.Maida Vale.8.Marylebone and Bayswater.9.Acknowledgements
